  <CalloutBox heading="For education Business Managers evaluating providers">
    <p>Before comparing proposals on price, ask each provider to produce their current WWCC register for the staff they intend to deploy. Ask them to walk you through their holiday clean program scope and pricing. Ask what documentation you will receive after each shift and how you access it. The answers to those three questions will tell you more than the price comparison will.</p>
